    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_d7c9744b">
            <div facs="#eSc_textblock_7ddb1b75" type="illustration">
                <figure>
                    <desc resp="#np">
                        A party, several couples dancing. Behind the window one can
                        see a grand piano.
                    </desc>
                </figure>
            </div>
            <head>
                <hi rendition="#i #c">
                    <lb />Summertime,-at home!
                </hi>
            </head>

            <p>
                <lb />
                <seg ana="#home #entertainment #hostess" resp="#np" type="topic">
                    <hi rendition="#k">Entertaining</hi> at home in the summertime is a very easy and a very enjoyable mat-
                    <lb />ter for the hostess who has a
                    <name type="brand">
                        Bush &amp; Lane Welte-Mignon (Licensce) Reproducing Piano.
                    </name>
                </seg>
            </p>

            <p>
                <seg ana="#entertainment" resp="#np" type="topic">
                    <lb /><hi rendition="#k">During</hi> dinner, guests are entertained by the most beautiful music of all time played
                    <lb />by practically all of the great pianists of the past two decades.
                </seg>
            </p>

            <p>
                <seg ana="#dance #popular #jazz" resp="#np" type="topic">
                    <lb /><hi rendition="#k">After</hi> dinner comes dancing, perhaps on the veranda, with the
                    <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon</name> provid-
                    <lb />ing the newest and most popular dance hits, played by a hundred masters of jazz.
                </seg>
            </p>

            <p>
                <lb /><hi rendition="#k">Really</hi>, with a
                <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon</name> at home, one has no desire and certainly no need to
                <lb />search elsewhere for a satisfactory place in which to entertain one's guests.
            </p>

            <p>
                <lb />
                <hi rend="#i">
                    Conventional Models Consistently Priced at
                    <measure commodity="wm" unit="dollar" quantity="1075">
                        $1075
                    </measure>
                    to
                    <measure commodity="wm" unit="dollar" quantity="4100">
                        $4100
                    </measure>
                </hi>
            </p>
